APPROACH 1B: Ordered Full-Factorial (Nested) Variations
- Enumerates the CARTESIAN PRODUCT of options across fields
- In a strict nested-loop order: Q1 outermost, then Q2, then Q3, ...
- This matches: "keep question 1 static, vary question 2..N; then next option in question 1..."
- WARNING: Full factorial here is HUGE (~129,024 combos). Excel (2 cols per combo) cannot hold that.
"""

